title: Yaroslav Ovsyannikov
text:
Yaroslav Valeryevich Ovsyannikov (; born 14 May 1993) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Dynamo%20Barnaul">FC Dynamo Barnaul</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Tom%20Tomsk">FC Tom Tomsk</a> on 12 March 2012 in a game against <a href="FC%20Volga%20Nizhny%20Novgorod">FC Volga Nizhny Novgorod</a>.
